lead_paragraph: Former world number one Luke Donald earned a berth in next week's U.S. Open at Oakmont following a playoff at a qualifying event in Powell, Ohio, on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Donald Grabs U.S. Open Berth in Ohio Playoff
